# Tell GitHub Linguist to ignore docs and config examples when calculating
# repository language statistics — they contain TypeScript code snippets
# from the original evoclaw architecture docs.

docs/**           linguist-documentation
config-examples/** linguist-documentation
assets/**         linguist-documentation
*.md              linguist-documentation
CHANGELOG.md      linguist-documentation
CONTRIBUTING.md   linguist-documentation
CONTRIBUTORS.md   linguist-documentation

# Dockerfile and shell are vendored/support files
setup.sh          linguist-vendored
launchd/**        linguist-vendored
